"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Aortogram shows a focal stenosis of the left renal artery with poststenotic dilatation (arrow). The right renal artery has a normal caliber and is delivering contrast to the right kidney well before the left kidney recieves contrast.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
